cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper is about natural language response suggestion using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also uses feed-forward neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves search optimization, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper is evaluating the method in a commercial e-mail application, which could be considered a topic in cybersecurity (cs.CY).
